item.title: CS130-lecture-20201028
item.description: 2-3 Tree # An empty tree is a 2-3 A BST is a 2-3 search tree no is yes Search miss Worst case running time for 2-3 tree search is O(lgn). Remember the height of a 2-3 tree is between (floor(\log_3 N)) and (floor(log_2 N)). So in the worst case it searches the entire height of the tree + 1. It inserts it into the 3 node to preserve the balance of the 2-3 tree.
